technological orientation may be particularly effective in guiding AI-
related workforce adjustments, but such director-level data are not
available in our setting. More broadly, it would be valuable to explore
whether the strategic-agility function of smaller boards extends to other
corporate decisions beyond AI workforce adoption, such as restructuring
or broader digital transformation. Addressing these questions would
require similarly granular, task-level or skill-level data that are not yet
available, but emerging datasets may allow researchers to assess
whether board-size effects generalize across different strategic margins.
